Interface IAuthorizationMessageSource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.wicket.validation.IErrorMessageSource, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthorizationMessageSource

    public interface IAuthorizationMessageSource
extends org.apache.wicket.validation.IErrorMessageSource, Serializable
    IErrorMessageSource which also knows which Component (if any) triggered this message and keeps track of variables that can be used by the message.
